Smit bụ aha nke nna nke ndi mba Dutch
Ọ na-anọchite anya mkpụrụ okwu ochie nke okwu Dutch "smid" maka "smith" (onye ọrụ ígwè) ma bụrụkwa Dutch nke aha nna Bekee Smith.

Ozi maka ugboro ole aha nna na MBA Netherlands na-ejedebe na njedebe nke ọnụ ọgụgụ zuru oke na-ewere n'afọ 1971.  Ozi kachasị ọhụrụ a na-enweta ngwa ngwa dabere na ọnụ ọgụgụ mmadụ nke afọ 1947, nke e mere ka ọha na eze nweta ma data ọnụ ọgụgụ na-enweghị isi na data aha aha

N'afọ 1947, e nwere mmadụ 29,783 e dekọrọ aha nna Smit, ebe ọnụ ọgụgụ mmadụ n'ozuzu ya nyere ọnụ ọgụgụ nke 9,519,000 dị ka ndị bi na 1947.  Na-arụ ọrụ na data a, enwere ike ịgbakọ ugboro ole aha Smit na Netherlands na 1947 ka ọ bụrụ ≈0.313% ma ọ bụ ≈3,130 nke 1,000,000 mmadụ ọ bụla.  Site n'iji ya tụnyere, aha nna Dutch a na-ahụkarị na data na afo 1947 bụ de Jong, nke nwere ugboro nke ≈0.580%.
Enwere ike iji ya tụnyere mba ndị na-asụ Bekee na afo 1998 dabere na nyocha nke National Trust

N'afọ 1998, a hụrụ ọnụọgụ kachasị elu na mba New Zealand dị ka 97.18 na nde mmadụ ọ bụla, ma ọ bụ ~ 1/30 nke ọnụego a hụrụ na Netherlands nke afọ 50 tupu.  N'etiti mba ndị a nyochara na nyocha National Trust, ọnụọgụ ndị metụtara maka 1991 bụ: New Zealand > Australia Canada ≫ United States > Northern Ireland > Great Britain > Republic of Ireland.  Nnukwu ọdịiche dị n'etiti Canada na United States gosipụtara na usoro a bụ ihe dịka okpukpu 3.5.
